msgstr "Monogram (PP)"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:548
msgid "Wordmark (PayPal)"
msgstr "Wordmark (PayPal)"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:549
msgid "Combination Mark (PP PayPal)"
msgstr "Kombinationsmärke (PP PayPal)"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:551
msgid ""
"Select the PayPal logo style displayed next to the payment method title on "
"the checkout page."
msgstr ""
"Välj den PayPal-logotypstil som visas bredvid betalningsmetodens titel på "
"kassan."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:554
msgid "Show Redirect Icon and Text"
msgstr "Visa omdirigeringsikon och text"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:558
msgid ""
"When enabled, a redirect icon and message will appear to let customers know "
"they will be taken to PayPal to complete their payment."
msgstr ""
"När det är aktiverat kommer en omdirigeringsikon och meddelande att visas "
"för att informera kunderna om att de kommer att tas till PayPal för att "
"slutföra sin betalning."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:561
msgid "Use Place Order Button"
msgstr "Använd knappen \"Placerar beställning\""

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:565
msgid ""
"Enable this to use the default Place Order button on the checkout page "
"instead of showing PayPal buttons. This setting does not affect Express "
"Checkout."
msgstr ""
"Aktivera detta för att använda standardknappen \"Placerar beställning\" på "
"kassan istället för att visa PayPal-knappar. Denna inställning påverkar inte "
"Express Checkout."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:713
msgid ""
"To use Advanced Card Payments, ensure your PayPal account is eligible and "
"enabled:<br><br>1. Visit developer.paypal.com → Apps & Credentials → API "
"Credentials.<br>2. Click your App Name.<br>3. Under \"Features\" → Accept "
"Payments, check if \"Advanced Credit and Debit Card Payments\" is enabled."
"<br>4. If missing, your account or region may not support it."
msgstr ""
"För att använda Advanced Card Payments, se till att ditt PayPal-konto är "
"berättigat och aktiverat:<br><br>1. Besök developer.paypal.com → Appar & "
"Behörigheter → API-uppgifter.<br>2. Klicka på ditt App-namn.<br>3. Under "
"\"Funktioner\" → Acceptera betalningar, kontrollera om \"Advanced Credit and "
"Debit Card Payments\" är aktiverat.<br>4. Om det saknas kan ditt konto eller "
"din region kanske inte stödja det."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:734
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:792
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:816
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1058
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1080
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1116
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1367
msgid "Important Note"
msgstr "Viktig notering"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:741
msgid "Enable Advanced Credit/Debit Card"
msgstr "Aktivera avancerat kredit-/betalkort"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:743
msgid ""
"Enable the Advanced Credit/Debit Card payment option as a separate gateway "
"on the checkout page. This gateway typically offers a lower PayPal fee "
"compared to the PayPal Smart Button. The fee is 2.59% + $0.49* per "
"transaction for Advanced Credit/Debit Card payments and 3.49% + $0.49* for "
"PayPal Smart Buttons. It supports major cards like Visa, Mastercard, and "
"American Express, providing a secure and streamlined payment experience."
msgstr ""
"Aktivera alternativet för avancerad kredit-/betalkortbetalning som en "
"separat gateway på kassan. Denna gateway erbjuder vanligtvis en lägre PayPal-"
"avgift jämfört med PayPal Smart Button. Avgiften är 2,59 % + $0,49* per "
"transaktion för avancerade kredit-/betalkortsbetalningar och 3,49 % + $0,49* "
"för PayPal Smart Buttons. Den stöder stora kort som Visa, Mastercard och "
"American Express, vilket ger en säker och smidig betalningsupplevelse."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:749
msgid ""
"Set the title for the Advanced Credit/Debit Card payment method as it will "
"appear on the checkout page (e.g., 'Pay with Credit/Debit Card').."
msgstr ""
"Ställ in titeln för betalningsmetoden för avancerat kredit-/betalkort som "
"den kommer att visas på kassan (t.ex. 'Betala med kredit-/betalkort')."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:750
msgid "Credit or Debit Card"
msgstr "Kredit- eller betalkort"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:754
msgid "Disable specific credit cards"
msgstr "Inaktivera specifika kreditkort"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:760
msgid ""
"By default all possible credit cards will be accepted. You can disable some "
"cards, if you wish."
msgstr ""
"Som standard kommer alla möjliga kreditkort att accepteras. Du kan "
"inaktivera vissa kort om du så önskar."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:767
msgid "Contingency for 3D Secure"
msgstr "Kontingens för 3D Secure"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:771
msgid "3D Secure when required"
msgstr "3D Secure när det krävs"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:772
msgid "Always trigger 3D Secure"
msgstr "Alltid aktivera 3D Secure"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:776
msgid ""
"3D Secure benefits cardholders and merchants by providing an additional "
"layer of verification using Verified by Visa, MasterCard SecureCode and "
"American Express SafeKey."
msgstr ""
"3D Secure gynnar kortinnehavare och handlare genom att erbjuda ett extra "
"lager av verifiering med hjälp av Verified by Visa, MasterCard SecureCode "
"och American Express SafeKey."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:779
msgid "Card Save Enabled"
msgstr "Kortbetalning aktiverad"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:780
msgid "Enable card saving at checkout"
msgstr "Aktivera kortbesparing vid kassan"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:783
msgid ""
"When enabled, customers can securely save their card details using PayPal "
"for faster future checkouts."
msgstr ""
"När det är aktiverat kan kunder säkert spara sina kortuppgifter med PayPal "
"för snabbare framtida utcheckningar."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:794
msgid ""
"Advanced Credit/Debit Card payments are not enabled in your PayPal account. "
"<br><br><strong>Supported Countries:</strong><br>Australia, Austria, "
"Belgium, Bulgaria, Canada, China, Cyprus, Czech Republic, Denmark, Estonia, "
"Finland, France, Germany, Greece, Hong Kong, Hungary, Ireland, Italy, Japan, "
"Latvia, Liechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxembourg, Malta, Netherlands, Norway, "
"Poland, Portugal, Romania, Singapore, Slovakia, Slovenia, Spain, Sweden, "
"United States, United Kingdom<br><br>"
msgstr ""
"Avancerade kredit-/betalkortsbetalningar är inte aktiverade i ditt PayPal-"
"konto. <br><br><strong>Stödda länder:</strong><br>Australien, Österrike, "
"Belgien, Bulgarien, Kanada, Kina, Cypern, Tjeckien, Danmark, Estland, "
"Finland, Frankrike, Tyskland, Grekland, Hongkong, Ungern, Irland, Italien, "
"Japan, Lettland, Liechtenstein, Litauen, Luxemburg, Malta, Nederländerna, "
"Norge, Polen, Portugal, Rumänien, Singapore, Slovakien, Slovenien, Spanien, "
"Sverige, USA, Storbritannien<br><br>"

